IPSLA - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-man-ipsla-oper:ipsla/

Retrieve operation of resource: ipsla

200 OK
ipsla_schema

Retrieve operation of resource: latest

operation-id: string
in path

200 OK
latest_schema

400 Bad Request

Internal Error
